            <p><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <orig>asy</orig><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <supplied reason="lost">Untel</supplied> fils de <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>litas, M<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>makhos fils de Deinis, 
